\id GEN - Dawuro Full Bible Latin Version 
\h Doometsaa 
\toc1 Doometsaa Mas'aafaa 
\toc2 Doometsaa 
\toc3 Dom. 
\mt1 Doometsaa Mas'aafaa 
\imt1 Geluwaa 
\ip Ha mas'aafay «Doometsaa» geetettiide s'eesetteedda gaasuu yewuwaa ubbaa doometsaa bessiyaa diraassa. 
\ip Doometsaabaa geetettiyaa mas'aafay ha alamii wooti med'etteeddentto: salotuunne sa'ay med'etteedda med'etaabaa, asaa zarii yeedda yuussaabaa, nagaraanne nagaraa maarotaabaa, anjjuunne shek'ay doometteedda doometsaabaa, S'oossaannanne asaa zaratuwaanna de'iyaa gaketetsaabaa odee. Doometsaabay laa"u huup'e gishuwaan shaakettiide s'eelettanaw danddayee. 
\ip Shemppuwaa ittuwaappe biide tammanne ittuwaa gakkanaw de'iyaa sa'ay, saluunne sa'ay med'etteedda med'etaabaanne asaa zariyaa koyro taarikiyaa odee. Addaamenne Hewaani taarikii, K'aayeelanne Aabeela taarikii, Nohenne bashshaa haatsaa taarikii, hewaadankka Baabloone Gimbbiyaa taarikii de'iyaawe ha shaakuwaana. 
\ip Shemppuwaa tammanne laa"uwaappe biide ishatamuwaa gakkanaw de'iyaa sa'ay Israa'eeliyaa asaw beni mayza aawotuwaa taarikiyaa odee. Unttuttu gidduwaan koyro bare ammanuwaaninne S'oossaw azazettiyaa hanotaan eretteeddawe Abrahaama. Hewaappe k'ay Aa na'aa Yisaak'a, Aa na'aa na'aa Yaak'oobanne Yaak'ooba naanaa tammanne laa"atuwaa taarikii kaalleedda. Hawanttu Yaak'ooba naanay tammanne laa"atuu, tammanne laa"u Israa'eeliyaa zaretoo ano gideeddawantta. Hawanttu ha tammanne laa"u Israa'eeliyaa naanatuwaa giddonkka Yooseefa dummayiide, hewaaddankka k'ay Yaak'oobanne Aa naanaa yenkkotuwaa unttuttu golle asaana Gibs'e gadiyaa afeedda hanotatuwaa minissiide s'eellee. 
\ip Ha mas'aafay asaa taarikiyaa odiyaawaa gidooppenne, ubbaappe aatsiide I odiyaawe S'oossay ootseedda oosuwaabaa. S'oossay salotuwaanne sa'aa med'd'eedda taarikiyaa oduwaa doommiide S'oossay bare asaw k'oppiyaawaa aggennawaa odiyaa hidootaan polee. Ha mas'aafaa giddon ha gas'aappe ya gas'aa gakkanaw odettiyaa taarikiyaa Goday, balabaa haniyaawantta pirddiyaawenne muriyaawe, bare asaa kaaletsiyaawenne maaddiyaawe, unttuttu taarikiyaa tangguwaakka giigissiyaawe bare huup'iyaan S'oossaa. Hawe beni mas'aafay s'aafetteeddawe asaa ammanuwaa taarikiyaa mazggabiide oyk'k'anaassanne he ammanuukka pas'a de'anaadan ootsanaassa. 
\iot Shemppatuwaa Ubbatoo Imetteedda K'antsa K'ofatuwaa 
\io1 Med'etaa Doometsaabaa \ior 1:1—2:3\ior* 
\io1 Eden Gennetiyaabaa \ior 2:4-25\ior* 
